#

Quick Refrigerator Pickles

10 min
$5
50 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganLow-CalorieGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

QuickNo-CookSnack

Description

Crisp and tangy, these quick refrigerator pickles are a refreshing addition to any meal!

Ingredients

  • cucumbers: 2 cups
  • white vinegar: 1 cup
  • water: 1 cup
  • sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic cloves: 2, sliced
  • dill sprigs: 4
  • mustard seeds: 1 teaspoon
  • black peppercorns: 1 teaspoon
  • red pepper flakes: 1/2 teaspoon
